33:23.198 --> 33:23.998
He must've gotten that on his

33:23.999 --> 33:25.399
own.

33:25.400 --> 33:26.200
And Danielle

33:26.201 --> 33:27.801
Marchetti?

33:27.802 --> 33:28.702
I don't know anything

33:28.703 --> 33:30.203
about that.

33:30.204 --> 33:31.471
In your medical

33:31.472 --> 33:33.406
opinion, is it possible Danielle

33:33.473 --> 33:35.941
died from a similar mixture?

33:36.009 --> 33:38.176
