33:38.244 --> 33:39.411
understand how that would've

33:39.412 --> 33:43.582
happened.

33:43.649 --> 33:46.651
But, uh, I would have to say

33:46.719 --> 33:51.257
yes, it's entirely possible.

33:53.961 --> 33:54.661
Thanks for seeing

33:54.662 --> 33:55.696
me again.

33:55.697 --> 33:57.598
Sure.

33:57.665 --> 33:59.299
How's it going with Patty?

33:59.300 --> 34:01.200
Well, um, she asked

34:01.202 --> 34:02.569
