34:24.223 --> 34:28.190
Thank you for smuggling this in.

34:28.259 --> 34:32.532
Wait.

34:32.599 --> 34:36.101
Stay and watch me eat it.

34:36.168 --> 34:37.502
And she made it

34:37.503 --> 34:39.471
seem like a test- like if I did

34:39.538 --> 34:40.572
it, she'd hire me.

34:40.572 --> 34:41.940
Did you do it?

34:41.940 --> 34:42.907
Yeah.

34:42.908 --> 34:43.773
Did she hire you?

34:43.774 --> 34:45.108
No.

34:45.109 --> 34:46.108
And she's acting like I don't

34:46.109 --> 34:47.310
exist.

34:47.311 --> 34:49.212
She won't meet with me, she's

34:49.280 --> 34:51.114
not returning my calls.

34:51.114 --> 34:53.014
What should I do?

34:55.386 --> 35:00.889
Run away.

35:00.957 --> 35:04.591
Seriously, far away.

35:04.659 --> 35:06.126
Forget about the job; forget

35:06.127 --> 35:09.096
about Patty.

35:14.702 --> 35:17.404
Hey, Joe returned the mink.

35:17.472 --> 35:18.305
He didn't give it to

35:18.306 --> 35:19.206
his mother?

35:19.207 --> 35:20.607
No, he threw it back in your

35:20.608 --> 35:21.775
face.

35:21.776 --> 35:23.676
He doesn't trust you.

35:25.947 --> 35:26.780
Then I don't trust

35:26.781 --> 35:28.982
him.

35:34.185 --> 35:35.784
Tommy, I miss

35:35.785 --> 35:38.585
anything?

35:38.653 --> 35:40.086
Just the choir.

35:40.087 --> 35:41.721
Band hasn't started playing yet.

35:41.722 --> 35:42.988
That's good.

35:42.989 --> 35:44.555
Wife would've cut my balls off

35:44.556 --> 35:47.655
if I missed this shit.

35:47.723 --> 35:50.056
I just flew in from

35:50.124 --> 35:51.324
Tucson.

35:51.325 --> 35:52.158
Don't even ask me what I shot

35:52.159 --> 35:54.026
in the back nine.

35:54.027 --> 35:55.327
You were out there

35:55.328 --> 35:56.595
playing golf?

35:56.596 --> 35:57.863
Yeah, just for the

35:57.864 --> 35:58.997
day.

35:58.998 --> 35:59.964
I like to hit the links once or

35:59.965 --> 36:01.666
twice a month.

36:01.667 --> 36:04.869
Thank God for a private plane.

36:04.937 --> 36:07.104
You took the jet?

36:07.172 --> 36:07.905
Well, how else you

36:07.906 --> 36:08.805
gonna be where you need to be

36:08.806 --> 36:10.474
when you need to be there?

36:10.475 --> 36:11.207
You should come with sometime,

36:11.208 --> 36:11.942
Tom.

36:11.943 --> 36:13.843
Do you some good to get away.

36:14.544 --> 36:17.447
Oh, shit.

36:17.514 --> 36:18.748
Turn off your ringer.

36:18.749 --> 36:19.582
Save my seat, would

36:19.583 --> 36:22.449
you?

36:22.517 --> 36:24.818
No cell phones.

36:33.059 --> 36:33.892
Say no more, I'll

36:33.893 --> 36:36.761
swing by on Thursday.

36:36.829 --> 36:38.029
Yeah, no problem.

36:38.030 --> 36:39.697
All right, we'll set it up.

36:39.698 --> 36:40.798
Hey, what's going on?

36:40.799 --> 36:42.534
Meeting Debbie here?

36:42.535 --> 36:43.701
