36:54.847 --> 36:55.747
Yeah, so?

36:55.748 --> 36:56.514
Did you know that

36:56.515 --> 36:57.181
Leverett was invested with

36:57.182 --> 36:57.882
Tobin?

36:57.883 --> 36:58.616
I didn't.

36:58.617 --> 36:59.450
You didn't want to

36:59.451 --> 37:00.184
know.

37:00.185 --> 37:00.918
You just wanted returns.

37:00.919 --> 37:01.752
I trusted you!

37:01.753 --> 37:02.753
Look, you gambled,

37:02.754 --> 37:03.588
you lost.

37:03.589 --> 37:04.956
Now stop crying about it.

37:04.957 --> 37:05.690
All right, just unload some

37:05.691 --> 37:07.425
assets and start all over again.

37:07.426 --> 37:09.393
Regroup, regrow, you could be

37:09.461 --> 37:10.761
back on your feet in no time.

37:10.762 --> 37:11.596
Don't give me that

37:11.597 --> 37:12.463
shit!

37:12.464 --> 37:13.564
Hey.

37:13.565 --> 37:15.465
You became a lawyer because you

37:15.533 --> 37:17.000
care about the rules?

37:17.001 --> 37:18.367
Who are you kidding?

37:18.368 --> 37:19.435
You're a rich little bitch and

37:19.436 --> 37:20.268
you had too much fun at the

37:20.269 --> 37:21.036
party and now you've got a

37:21.037 --> 37:21.736
hangover.

37:21.737 --> 37:23.637
Grow up, it happens.

37:36.116 --> 37:36.849
Hello?

37:36.850 --> 37:37.683
Hey, it's Alex

37:37.684 --> 37:38.450
Benjamin, you'll never believe

37:38.451 --> 37:39.351
this.

37:39.352 --> 37:40.285
Patty just called and she hired

37:40.286 --> 37:42.120
me.

37:42.121 --> 37:43.521
Oh, really?

37:43.522 --> 37:45.389
Congratulations, that's, that's

37:45.390 --> 37:46.657
amazing.

37:46.658 --> 37:47.390
Anyway, thanks for

37:47.391 --> 37:48.557
your help.

37:48.558 --> 37:50.557
You're welcome.

37:50.625 --> 37:52.856
Good luck, Alex.

38:15.069 --> 38:16.069
You're staying in a

38:16.070 --> 38:18.437
