38:44.196 --> 38:44.996
Now I don't know if I can trust

38:44.997 --> 38:46.897
you, Joe.

38:46.965 --> 38:49.933
And I can trust you?

38:50.001 --> 38:50.934
Your father always

38:50.935 --> 38:55.805
