38:55.873 --> 38:57.140
The fur had nothing to do with

38:57.141 --> 38:59.076
you or me.

38:59.143 --> 39:01.647
It was for your mother.

39:05.118 --> 39:07.352
Listen, just...

39:10.990 --> 39:12.057
Look in the bottom dresser

39:12.058 --> 39:14.626
drawer.

39:46.361 --> 39:47.896
Patty, I'm at

39:47.897 --> 39:49.429
Farmingdale Airport.

39:49.430 --> 39:50.362
Why? What's up?

39:50.363 --> 39:51.896
I had a talk with a

39:51.897 --> 39:53.528
guy who owns a private jet and

39:53.529 --> 39:55.259
that gave me an idea.

39:55.260 --> 39:56.426
About what?

39:56.427 --> 39:57.125
I think I know who

39:57.126 --> 39:58.224
the Tobins used to move money

39:58.225 --> 39:59.523
into the Caribbean.

39:59.524 --> 40:00.557
Yeah?

40:00.558 --> 40:03.659
Danielle Marchetti's
daughter.

